    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on some annual reviews for my team. Quick question: what's the actual professional difference between telling someone they \"need improvement\" vs \"have developmental opportunities\"? I want to make sure I'm not being too harsh but also being clear. Thanks.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
